505-344-8139 (phone)        </p>
<p><a href="http://www.page1book.com/">Page One Books</a><br />
11018 Montgomery NE<br />
Albuquerque, NM, 87111.<br />
505-294-2026</p>
<p><strong>Misc. stuff:</strong></p>
<p>Pastian&#8217;s Bakery<br />
3320 2nd St NW<br />
